    "The original YOLOv7 has 314 A satisfactory performance increase was achieved with a small increase in complexity in the model.Table 3 Evaluation metrics of the teeth numbering and caries detection model Recall Precision F1-score Left side teeth numbering 0.976 0.978 0.977 Right side teeth numbering 0.972 0.993 0.982 Left side caries detection 0.857 0.833 0.844 Right side caries detection 0.810 0.900 0.800 Left side-numbering and caries detection 0.966 0.966 0.966 Right side-numbering and caries detection 0.959 0.985 0.968 Left and right-side numbering and caries detection-All 0.962 0.975 0.967 Teeth numbering-All 0.974 0.985 0.979 Caries detection-All 0.833 0.866 0.849 Table 4 Evaluation metrics of the teeth numbering and caries detection matching model TP FP FN TN Accuracy Recall Specificity Precision F1-score Left side 240 48 47 1102 0.933 0.836 0.958 0.833 0.834 Right side 260 30 66 1049 0.931 0.797 0.972 0.896 0.843 All 500 78 113 2151 0.932 0.815 0.965 0.865 0.839 DiscussionIn dentistry, achieving an accurate and precise diagnosis of dental caries is essential for the primary step towards successful treatment implementation.",
    "Dental caries diagnosis methods aim to improve the diagnostic process by facilitating the early detection of caries or enabling its objective identification [55].",
    "Although tooth detection and numbering may seem straightforward, the accuracy of tooth numbering and caries detection can be affected by the limited and diverse knowledge of novice clinicians, potentially resulting in inconsistent diagnoses and inadequate treatment approaches.",
